snippet.title: Quake mod Unforgiven rendered in qbism Super8
snippet.description:
Unforgiven 3, a huge Quake 1 single-player map by Tronyn and modded by PM, rendered by the qbism Super8 game engine.  Demonstrates fisheye lens, RPG 3rd person view, skybox, and custom palette.  And lots and lots of monsters!  Happy Halloween.
Get the map/mod: http://www.quaddicted.com/reviews/unforgiven.html
Read about it:  http://celephais.net/board/view_thread.php?id=60545
Get qbism Super8:  http://qbism.com
